My stomach hurts.

18:16.387 --> 18:18.639
Not now, son.

18:18.681 --> 18:20.140
That your kid?

18:20.182 --> 18:21.183
Yes, why?

18:21.225 --> 18:22.560
This guy has been

18:22.602 --> 18:24.311
collecting money

18:22.602 --> 18:24.311
for his own kid.

