What?

18:25.563 --> 18:27.857
Dewey, did you tell

18:25.563 --> 18:27.857
these people...?

18:27.899 --> 18:29.609
What the hell

18:27.899 --> 18:29.609
you trying to

18:27.899 --> 18:29.609
pull here, mister?

18:29.650 --> 18:32.236
He's been yanking our chain!

18:32.278 --> 18:34.154
No, no, no, no, no. Wait, wait,

18:32.278 --> 18:34.154
wait, wait, wait, wait.

