REESE:

18:41.203 --> 18:42.162
Ow, ow, ow...

18:42.204 --> 18:43.247
Is this your son?

18:43.289 --> 18:44.331
Reese?

18:44.373 --> 18:45.959
He was running

18:44.373 --> 18:45.959
a black market.

