Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

18:52.840 --> 18:55.175
Now, now, now, wait

18:52.840 --> 18:55.175
just a second.

18:55.217 --> 18:56.176
I know how this must look.

18:56.218 --> 18:57.845
But if you just give me

18:56.218 --> 18:57.845
the chance

18:57.887 --> 18:59.179
to get to the bottom of this,

18:59.221 --> 19:00.974
I swear to you,

18:59.221 --> 19:00.974
I will make this right.

19:01.015 --> 19:02.100
Come over here.

19:02.141 --> 19:04.184
You boys have both behaved

19:02.141 --> 19:04.184
very badly.

19:04.226 --> 19:06.353
So, you are both going

19:04.226 --> 19:06.353
to apologize

19:06.395 --> 19:08.230
to these nice, generous people

19:08.272 --> 19:10.566
like you have never

19:08.272 --> 19:10.566
apologized before.

19:10.608 --> 19:12.192
Do you hear me?

19:12.234 --> 19:14.194
Okay.

19:14.236 --> 19:16.196
Dewey, come on.

19:16.238 --> 19:17.197
Go ahead.

19:17.239 --> 19:18.491
Nice and loud.

19:18.532 --> 19:21.285
We're sorry we left

19:18.532 --> 19:21.285
the couch on the tracks

19:21.327 --> 19:23.203
and wrecked the train.

19:23.245 --> 19:24.914
(gasping)

19:30.169 --> 19:32.212
Reese, run, run.

19:32.254 --> 19:34.214
JERRY:

19:32.254 --> 19:34.214
Hey, stop him.

19:34.256 --> 19:36.175
(Hal yelling)

19:39.137 --> 19:42.306
Well, this is it.

19:42.348 --> 19:44.224
Maybe I'll call you sometime.

19:44.266 --> 19:45.643
Whatever.

19:50.148 --> 19:51.231
Hey, I, uh...

19:51.273 --> 19:53.151
I actually had

19:51.273 --> 19:53.151
a good time.

19:53.192 --> 19:54.234
Me, too.

19:54.276 --> 19:56.737
You're, like,

19:54.276 --> 19:56.737
a really good

19:54.276 --> 19:56.737
girlfriend.

19:56.779 --> 19:58.197
Thanks.

20:02.994 --> 20:04.411
Hey, sorry about tonight.

20:04.453 --> 20:07.832
Yeah, well, your plan

20:04.453 --> 20:07.832
to palm me off on a 12-

20:04.453 --> 20:07.832
year-old backfired,

20:07.874 --> 20:09.959
'cause I actually had

20:07.874 --> 20:09.959
