20:10.001 --> 20:11.460
Well, good for you,

20:10.001 --> 20:11.460
Poodlehead.

20:11.502 --> 20:12.753
You know what?

20:12.795 --> 20:15.255
I don't care about your

20:12.795 --> 20:15.255
childish taunts anymore.

20:15.297 --> 20:17.257
You can call me

20:15.297 --> 20:17.257
anything you like.

20:17.299 --> 20:19.259
I think I'll stick

20:17.299 --> 20:19.259
with Poodlehead.

20:19.301 --> 20:21.261
Fine.

20:21.303 --> 20:24.140
I'm glad it doesn't bother you

20:21.303 --> 20:24.140
when I call you "Poodlehead,"

20:24.182 --> 20:25.766
Poodlehead.

20:25.808 --> 20:27.351
I got to tell you,

20:25.808 --> 20:27.351
Poodlehead...

20:27.393 --> 20:28.936
Shut up!

20:28.978 --> 20:32.314
Do not set foot

20:28.978 --> 20:32.314
outside this area.

20:32.356 --> 20:34.274
Not one foot.

20:34.316 --> 20:35.985
I would just like

20:34.316 --> 20:35.985
to get one thing clear.

20:36.027 --> 20:38.362
When we go home,

20:36.027 --> 20:38.362
you fellas are still going to be

20:38.404 --> 20:40.280
a presence

20:38.404 --> 20:40.280
in the community, right?

20:40.322 --> 20:44.994
If I wasn't in uniform,

20:40.322 --> 20:44.994
I'd take a swing at you, myself.

20:45.036 --> 20:45.953
Fair enough.

