LOIS:

20:45.995 --> 20:47.663
Are you telling me

20:47.705 --> 20:50.290
that I can't discipline

20:47.705 --> 20:50.290
my own child?

20:50.332 --> 20:52.126
Lady, we got a lot

20:50.332 --> 20:52.126
