21:12.354 --> 21:13.564
What did  we  do?

21:13.606 --> 21:15.608
Maybe Malcolm can bring us

21:13.606 --> 21:15.608
a couple blankets.

21:15.649 --> 21:16.984
Come on.

21:18.360 --> 21:19.319
Malcolm.

21:19.361 --> 21:21.363
Can you get us some blankets?

21:21.405 --> 21:23.032
LOIS:

21:21.405 --> 21:23.032
Help us out here.

